{"title":"忆读《讲话》","authors":["杨雪"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":5,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆读《讲话》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是穿越迷茫的最佳方式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火把一样明亮的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀我们的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们远离歧途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步履坚定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些光芒升华的恒温"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们在迷蒙的风雪里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咀嚼温暖的含义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象那些美好的情景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻过冬天和夜晚的章节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的芬芳扑进眼底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉重的心情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羽毛一样纷纷脱落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"植物站立生长的姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"构成我们一生的品格"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}